title: A10 Loadbalancer: System Temperature
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/a10
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the system temperature of A10 Networks ADC
 loadbalancers via SNMP (A10-AX-MIB, axSyshwPhySystemTemp).

 Upper warning and critical levels can be configured via the rule
 "Temperature". Without configuration the check reports {OK}.

discovery:
 One service with the item "System" is created.

item:
 The fixed string "System".
